!! Trouble Shooting

!!! Unable to load a file

If you drag in a file from the root of your Wiki folder and it doesn't load, then try using a relative path with `. /` as a prefix. For example, go into edit mode and change a path from `file://A File.pdf` to a path like `file://./A File.pdf` then it may be fixed.